41:33.330 --> 41:34.650
Macam mana orang ini?

41:34.900 --> 41:35.650
Betul.

41:36.500 --> 41:37.250
Pergi.

41:44.130 --> 41:45.420
Helo, hai.

41:45.860 --> 41:47.020
Maaf, minta tolong.

41:47.420 --> 41:49.020
Tak sangka kami mengganggu

41:49.020 --> 41:49.900
